{"tid":652473,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"死咗隻貓有乜有不了","createTime":"2018-05-04T00:50:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T15:02:55.000Z","uid":37651,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9705350e19733cd7e23772c1ac213d38f4d58827","tid":652473,"uid":37651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T00:50:13.000Z","msg":"點解成三十幾歲人仲可以喊得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我好掛住你"},{"pid":"20d06ea346a333ea7664518f56720151037583bc","tid":652473,"uid":162906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T01:03:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都係咁..."},{"pid":"4a274d709353f3bf34c9c9abba7bf59b0f67fb1d","tid":652473,"uid":73730,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T01:05:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n岩岩今朝我有隻狗死左<br />\n<br />\n但我覺得都算好<br />\n佢死前已經行唔到路<br />\n而且死時過程唔太長 一晚時間就突然走左<br />\n同埋佢起碼係係自己屋企 熟悉既環境 同係佢最鍾意既（我媽）身邊走<br />\n<br />\n宜家係我呀媽屋企 等緊人黎收佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94648a51c930b72a42c7a5c778a858875621bc27","tid":652473,"uid":73730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T01:07:14.000Z","msg":"我一朝早起身睇到喊左出黎<br />\n宜家慢慢平復左<br />\n<br />\n帶左另一隻狗番呀媽到<br />\n隻衰野仲淨係掛住玩 想打柒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b87d75e4dda6195fda60b3f94a3ee2c611110efd","tid":652473,"uid":37651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T01:26:40.000Z","msg":"係公司做梗野但眼淚自己不停咁流,好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81376a4fbdfd2933b0aa96d370f06ca9b7a01585","tid":652473,"uid":4780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T01:35:21.000Z","msg":"Rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n放心啦巴打，佢地去到上面會好開心有好野朋友陪佢地玩陪佢地跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我隻狗都快9歲了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b0a6e790bdee57b96c681d2d98c8f26e387a30f","tid":652473,"uid":37651,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T01:05:04.000Z","msg":"尋日火化了,臨火化前見佢最後一面時，我一邊摸佢眼淚就不停咁流,直至火化結束後,心情已經平伏咗好多,終於了結咗件心事<br />\n<br />\n後話:我尋晚瞓唔著覺眼光光,突然聞到一絲我隻貓既氣味,因為係由無到有之後就無,所以&quot;我覺得&quot;唔係錯覺<br />\n<br />\n貓貓你陪多我一陣,之後你就出去識女仔喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13f03ea934acddb713f7eb44f1f025f007232635","tid":652473,"uid":133166,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1b0a6e790bdee57b96c681d2d98c8f26e387a30f","tid":652473,"uid":37651,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T01:05:04.000Z","msg":"尋日火化了,臨火化前見佢最後一面時，我一邊摸佢眼淚就不停咁流,直至火化結束後,心情已經平伏咗好多,終於了結咗件心事<br />\n<br />\n後話:我尋晚瞓唔著覺眼光光,突然聞到一絲我隻貓既氣味,因為係由無到有之後就無,所以&quot;我覺得&quot;唔係錯覺<br />\n<br />\n貓貓你陪多我一陣,之後你就出去識女仔喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T11:37:31.000Z","msg":"我果時係火化之前見隻狗最後一面冇喊到, 應該話果時仲未相送佢果時真係死左.<br />\n到D工作人員放左佢入爐, 見到D火光同D爐聲先知道佢真係死左, 果一下先喊出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"994113c5f013939fc65be39a6106ffebfd4541c8","tid":652473,"uid":30457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T11:49:32.000Z","msg":"我隻狗尋晚都走左，佢陪左我15年 <br />\n連最後一句都講唔切就走左<br />\n好掛住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51e78ecf623591b75a364481557b69ccd53259ad","tid":652473,"uid":37651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"994113c5f013939fc65be39a6106ffebfd4541c8","tid":652473,"uid":30457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T11:49:32.000Z","msg":"我隻狗尋晚都走左，佢陪左我15年 <br />\n連最後一句都講唔切就走左<br />\n好掛住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T12:09:58.000Z","msg":"佢能夠係你身邊渡過佢一生，已經係好幸福，佢已經畢業喇<br />\n<br />\n希望你都可以快啲收拾心情<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5482d932697135b47ae0de1eb070ee0e3129ae8d","tid":652473,"uid":37651,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T12:33:26.000Z","msg":"以前都唔明啲人只係死一隻寵物點解會好似死咗親人咁，有乜好喊<br />\n<br />\n到發生係自己身上時，就明白佢真係自己好細佬好朋友，係寂寞夜晚有佢陪伴，唔開心時佢會烘塊面埋黎，有時會怪佢啲爪整傷我，又有時會嬲佢周為痾，但已經再無機會摸佢鍚佢了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係臨火化前陪佢最後半小時，我一邊摸佢已經冰冷身體，眼淚就不停咁流，不斷想起一齊生活畫面，我聞佢身體嘅氣味怕自己會忘記，臨推去火化前我錫咗佢面額一下<br />\n<br />\n我以後都唔可再見到佢了"},{"pid":"cc479a1935ed06c6bef3753c91f3392f3f93ed65","tid":652473,"uid":24139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5482d932697135b47ae0de1eb070ee0e3129ae8d","tid":652473,"uid":37651,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T12:33:26.000Z","msg":"以前都唔明啲人只係死一隻寵物點解會好似死咗親人咁，有乜好喊<br />\n<br />\n到發生係自己身上時，就明白佢真係自己好細佬好朋友，係寂寞夜晚有佢陪伴，唔開心時佢會烘塊面埋黎，有時會怪佢啲爪整傷我，又有時會嬲佢周為痾，但已經再無機會摸佢鍚佢了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係臨火化前陪佢最後半小時，我一邊摸佢已經冰冷身體，眼淚就不停咁流，不斷想起一齊生活畫面，我聞佢身體嘅氣味怕自己會忘記，臨推去火化前我錫咗佢面額一下<br />\n<br />\n我以後都唔可再見到佢了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T14:31:58.000Z","msg":"好重洋蔥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打要堅強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我當年失去隻愛寵都係喊到收唔聲"},{"pid":"3ade23ddd5db56ebaa4a7aead260